  "body": "Currently when you execute a debug session within the Truffle develop console using `debug <tx id>`, it automatically compiles and migrates the current project before entering a debug session, which is heralded by the appearance of the debug command summary.\r\n\r\nHow can we debug the construction of a smart contract during a deployment/migration?  If this is not possible yet, I would like to make this a feature suggestion.",
